{
  "Rotational Inertia": "旋转惯性",
  "This lesson covers the fundamental measures of center used to analyze and summarize data sets. You'll learn how to calculate and apply the mean, median, and mode, and understand when each is most appropriate.": "这个课程涵盖了分析和总结数据集的中心的基本测量方法。 您将学会如何计算和应用平均值、 中位数和模式, 并了解何时最合适 。",
  "What is the moment of inertia of a point mass of 3 kg located 2 m from the axis of rotation?": "距离旋转轴2米的3公斤点质量的惯性时间是多少?",
  "I = mr² = 3 × 2² = 3 × 4 = 12 kg·m².": "I=2 = 3 × 22 = 3 × 4 = 12 公斤/平方米。",
  "What is the moment of inertia of a solid disk of mass 4 kg and radius 0.5 m about its central axis?": "4千克质量和半径0.5米的固体圆盘中央轴的惯性是什么时刻?",
  "I = ½MR² = ½(4)(0.25) = 0.5 kg·m².": "I = 1⁄2 MR2 = 1⁄2 (4) (0.25) = 0.5kg.m2 = 0.5kg.m2。",
  "A thin hoop of mass 2 kg and radius 0.3 m rotates about its central axis. What is its moment of inertia?": "2千克质量和半径0.3米的细环围绕其中轴旋转。其惯性时刻是什么?",
  "For a hoop: I = MR² = 2 × (0.3)² = 2 × 0.09 = 0.18 kg·m².": "套圈:I = MR2 = 2 × (0.3)2 = 2 × 0.09 = 0.18 千克/平方米。",
  "Using the parallel axis theorem, if a disk has I_cm = 0.5 kg·m², mass 4 kg, and is rotated about an axis 1 m from its center, what is I?": "使用平行轴定理, 如果磁盘I_ cm = 0.5kggm2, 质量 4kg, 并且从中心旋转轴1米左右, 我是什么 ?",
  "Parallel axis theorem: I = I_cm + Md² = 0.5 + 4(1²) = 0.5 + 4 = 4.5 kg·m².": "平行轴定理:I = I_cm + Md2 = 0.5 + 4(12) = 0.5 + 4 = 4.5 千克/平方米。",
  "A solid sphere has mass 5 kg and radius 0.2 m. What is its moment of inertia about a diameter?": "固体球体的重量为5公斤,半径为0.2米。 其直径的惯性时间是什么?",
  "I = (2/5)MR² = (2/5)(5)(0.04) = 0.08 kg·m².": "I = (2/5) MR2 = (2/5)(5)(0.04) = 0.08 公斤/平方米。",
  "A uniform thin rod of mass 3 kg and length 2 m is rotated about its center. What is its moment of inertia?": "一条3公斤重和2米长的穿制服的薄杆,在中间旋转。它的惯性是什么时刻?",
  "I = (1/12)ML² = (1/12)(3)(4) = 1 kg·m².": "I = (1/12)ML2 = (1/12)(3)(4) = 1千克/平方米。",
  "The same 3 kg, 2 m rod is rotated about one end. What is its moment of inertia?": "同样的3公斤,2米杆旋转大约一端。它的惯性是什么时刻?",
  "I = (1/3)ML² = (1/3)(3)(4) = 4 kg·m².": "I = (1/3) ML2 = (1/3)(3)(4) = 4kg mm2。",
  "Two point masses, 2 kg each, are connected by a massless rod 1 m long and rotate about the center. What is the total I?": "两点质量,每点2公斤,由一条1米长的无质量杆连接,在中心旋转。总计是多少?",
  "Each mass is 0.5 m from the center. I_total = m₁r₁² + m₂r₂² = 2(0.5)² + 2(0.5)² = 0.5 + 0.5 = 1.0 kg·m².": "每质量距离中间0.5米。I_总计=m1r12+m2r22=2(0.5)2+2(0.5)2=0.5+0.5=0.5=1.0千克/m2。",
  "What is moment of inertia?": "什么是惯性的时刻?",
  "Moment of inertia (I) is the rotational analog of mass. It quantifies how difficult it is to change an object's rotational motion, depending on mass distribution relative to the axis.": "惯性动力( I) 是质量的旋转类比。 它量化改变对象的旋转运动有多困难, 取决于相对于轴的质量分布 。",
  "What is the parallel axis theorem?": "平行轴定理是什么?",
  "The parallel axis theorem states I = I_cm + Md², where d is the distance between the center-of-mass axis and the new parallel axis. It always increases I relative to the center of mass.": "平行轴定理表示 I = I_ cm + Md2, 其中 d 是主轴中心与新的平行轴之间的距离。 它总是使I 相对于质量中心增加 。",
  "What is the perpendicular axis theorem?": "垂直轴定理是什么?",
  "The perpendicular axis theorem applies to planar (flat) objects: I_z = I_x + I_y, where z is perpendicular to the plane and x, y are in the plane.": "垂直轴定理适用于平面(平面)物体:I_z = I_x + I_y,其中 z 与平面垂直, x, y 在平面上。",
  "What is a 'principal axis' of rotation?": "什么是旋转的主轴?",
  "A principal axis is one about which the angular momentum and angular velocity are parallel. Products of inertia are zero, and the object rotates without wobbling.": "主轴是角动和角速度平行的轴。惯性产品为零,物体旋转时不动。",
  "What is the formula for the moment of inertia of a continuous body?": "一个连续体的惯性时刻的公式是什么?",
  "For a continuous mass distribution, I = ∫ r² dm, where r is the perpendicular distance from each mass element dm to the axis of rotation.": "对于连续质量分布,I =  r2 dm, r 是每个质量元素 dm 到旋转轴的垂直距离。",
  "What is the difference between a solid cylinder and a hollow cylinder of the same mass and radius in terms of I?": "就我而言,一个固体气瓶和一个质量和半径相同的空气瓶之间有什么区别?",
  "Solid cylinder: I = ½MR². Hollow (thin-walled) cylinder: I = MR². The hollow cylinder has twice the I because all mass is at maximum distance from the axis.": "固体圆柱体:I = 1⁄2 MR2. 空(隔墙)圆柱体:I = MR2. 空圆柱体为I的两倍,因为所有质量都处于轴的最大距离。",
  "A 2 kg uniform disk (R = 0.15 m) is mounted on an axle 0.25 m from its center using the parallel axis theorem. What is I about the axle?": "一个2千克的统一磁盘(R = 0.15米)用平行轴定理从中心以轴0.25米的速度安装在轴上。对于轴,我有什么看法?",
  "I_cm = ½MR² = ½(2)(0.0225) = 0.0225 kg·m². I = I_cm + Md² = 0.0225 + 2(0.0625) = 0.0225 + 0.125 = 0.1475 kg·m².": "I_cm = 1⁄2 MR2 = 1⁄2 (2) 0.0225 = 0.0225 千克/平方米.I = I_cm + Md2 = 0.0225 + 2.0625 + 0.0225 = 0.0225 + 0.125 = 0.475 千克/平方米。",
  "Two identical solid spheres (each 1 kg, radius 0.05 m) are connected by a 0.4 m massless rod and rotated about the center of the rod. What is I_total?": "两个相同的固态球体(每1公斤,半径0.05米)由0.4米无质量棒连接,在杆中央旋转。",
  "Each sphere: I_cm = (2/5)(1)(0.0025) = 0.001 kg·m². Distance from center of rod to sphere center: d = 0.2 m. By parallel axis theorem: I_each = 0.001 + 1(0.04) = 0.041. I_total = 2 × 0.041 = 0.082 kg·m².": "每一球体: I_cm = (2/5(1)(0.0025) = 0.001千克/m2. 从杆中心到球中心之间的距离: d = 0.2米。按平行轴定理: I_each = 0.001 + 1,0.04 = 0.041。 I_ 总计 = 2 × 0.041 = 0.082千克/m2。",
  "A flywheel has I = 8 kg·m² and rotates at 300 RPM. What is its rotational kinetic energy?": "飞轮I=8kg/m2,在300RPM旋转。 它的旋转动能是什么?",
  "ω = 300 × 2π/60 = 10π rad/s. KE = ½Iω² = ½(8)(100π²) = 400π² ≈ 3,950 J.": "= 300 × 2/60 = 10 rad/s. KE = 1⁄2I= 2 = 1⁄2(8) (1002) = 4002 = 3 950 J.",
  "A composite object consists of a solid disk (mass 3 kg, radius 0.2 m) with a point mass of 1 kg attached at the rim. What is the total I about the disk's center?": "复合物体由硬盘组成(质量为3公斤,半径为0.2米),其点质量为1公斤,附在边缘。",
  "I_disk = ½(3)(0.04) = 0.06 kg·m². I_point = 1 × (0.2)² = 0.04 kg·m². I_total = 0.06 + 0.04 = 0.10 kg·m².": "I_disk = 1⁄2(3)/0.04 = 0.06 kg/m2 I_point = 1 × (0.2)2 = 0.04 kg/m2 I_ 总计 = 0.06 + 0.04 = 0.10 千克/m2。",
  "A uniform door (mass 12 kg, width 0.9 m) is modeled as a thin rectangular slab rotating about its hinges. What is its moment of inertia? (I = ⅓ML² for a rod about one end)": "统一的门( 12公斤, 宽度为 0. 9 米) , 以一个细长的矩形板为模型, 围绕其锁链旋转。 它的惯性是什么时刻? (I = 1⁄3ML2 指一端的杆)",
  "Treating the door as a slab rotating about one edge: I = (1/3)Mw² = (1/3)(12)(0.81) = (1/3)(9.72) = 3.24 kg·m².": "将门当作旋转在一个边缘的板块:I = (1/3)Mw2 = (1/3)(12)0.81 = (1/3)(9.72) = 3.24公斤/平方米。"
}